definition: many/much/often/a lot of/numerous/more/in excess/how (to what extent)/multi-/Taiwan pr. [duo2] when it means "how"

sentences.english: Yet the dominoes may not fall so fast.
sentences.chinese: 然而這份多米諾骨牌並不會倒地如此之快。

sentences.english: The manager hasn't worked out a suitable action to reduce the domino effect.
sentences.chinese: 經理還沒有想出一個適合的舉措來裁汰多米諾效應。

sentences.english: An improved high fan-in domino circuit is proposed.
sentences.chinese: 設計實現了一種改進的高扇入多米諾電路結構。

sentences.english: This domino effect can be avoided by using domain specialization.
sentences.chinese: 可以使用領域專門化來避免這種多米諾骨牌效應。

sentences.english: They set up over 3.40 million dominoes.
sentences.chinese: 他們搭建了三百四十萬個多米諾骨牌。

sentences.english: The Domino Doctrine and Weapons of mass destruction should be examined in the same segment.
sentences.chinese: 多米諾理論和大殺器應該在同一段檢驗。
冰島語中多米諾骨牌怎麼說？

sentences.english: That will be the trigger for so many dominoes to fall.
sentences.chinese: 這將引發一系列多米諾骨牌效應。

sentences.english: It is illegal to play Dominos on Sunday.
sentences.chinese: 日曜日玩多米諾骨牌違法。

sentences.english: There is a domino or ricochet effect that is building.
sentences.chinese: 正在聚集多米諾骨牌或者“彈跳”效應。
